<h5>Magical Realism: A Window into Colombia‚Äôs Soul</h5>
   
	<p>	
	Magical realism is one of the most defining literary styles of Latin America, 
	and perhaps no one embodies it better than Gabriel Garc√≠a M√°rquez. This genre blends
	the ordinary with the extraordinary, presenting magical elements as part of everyday life. 
	In Colombia, magical realism is not just a literary device‚Äîit is a way of understanding the world,
	deeply rooted in the country‚Äôs history, culture, and social fabric.</p>
	
	

<h5>What is magical realism?</h5>
<img src="https://www.lifeder.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/realismo-magico-lifeder-libro-min.jpg" 
         alt="Realismo M√°gico" 
